[h1]🛠️ Mod Settings[/h1]
You can adjust mod settings directly in the game Options menu:
[list]
[*] [b]Include Temperature in "Lacks Resources" Warning:[/b] Toggle whether the yellow "Lacks Resources" warning takes your temperature limits into account (turn off for maximum late-game performance).
[*] [b]Apply Limits to Construction Materials:[/b] Toggle whether temperature limits also apply to materials delivered to build new structures (prevents using hot materials in cold-area construction).
[/list]

